0 hover:border-accent hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\">Режем</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wider px-4 py-2 border border-white/20 hover:border-accent hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\">Красим</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[11px] text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wider px-4 py-2 border border-white/20 hover:border-accent hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\">Собираем</span></div><div class=\"mt-10 space-y-4 border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-5\"><p class=\"text-white/70 text-base leading-relaxed font-medium\">Более 5 лет радуем клиентов качественным металлом.</p><p class=\"text-white/60 text-base leading-relaxed\">Выполним работу любой сложности и предложим решение для любого кошелька!</p></div><a href=\"#gallery\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-10 py-5 mt-12 bg-white/5 hover:bg-accent/20 border-2 border-white/20 hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300 group min-w-[280px]\"><span class=\"font-bold text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide\">Наши работы</span></a></div><div class=\"lg:self-start\"><form class=\"reveal-x bg-white p-8 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-12 h-12 border-l-2 border-t-2 border-accent/30 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-300\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-12 h-12 border-r-2 border-t-2 border-accent/30 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-300\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-12 h-12 border-l-2 border-b-2 border-accent/30 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-300\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-12 h-12 border-r-2 border-b-2 border-accent/30 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative mb-8\"><div class=\"absolute -left-2 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-accent to-accent-h\"></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl font-black text-text uppercase tracking-wider pl-4\">Получить консультацию</h3></div><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div><label class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block\">Имя *</label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full border-2 border-border px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text bg-bg focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:bg-white transition-all placeholder:text-muted\" placeholder=\"Ваше имя\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block\">Телефон *</label><input type=\"tel\" required=\"\" inputMode=\"tel\" pattern=\"[+0-9()\\-\\s]{10,20}\" title=\"Введите корректный номер телефона\" class=\"w-full border-2 border-border px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text bg-bg focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:bg-white transition-all placeholder:text-muted\" placeholder=\"+7 (999) 123-45-67\" name=\"phone\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block\">Email</label><input type=\"email\" class=\"w-full border-2 border-border px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text bg-bg focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:bg-white transition-all placeholder:text-muted\" placeholder=\"example@example.com\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block\">Описание проекта</label><textarea name=\"description\" rows=\"3\" class=\"w-full border-2 border-border px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text bg-bg focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:bg-white transition-all resize-none placeholder:text-muted\" placeholder=\"Расскажите о вашем проекте\"></textarea></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 pt-2\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"agreed\" required=\"\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 border-2 border-border accent-accent cursor-pointer\" name=\"agreed\"/><label for=\"agreed\" class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-muted leading-relaxed\">Я согласен на обработку персональных данных в соответствии с<!-- --> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-accent hover:text-accent-h transition-colors underline\">политикой конфиденциальности</a></label></div></div><button class=\"font-display font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-none transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden group disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:hover:shadow-none bg-accent text-white hover:bg-accent-h hover:shadow-accent px-8 py-3 text-sm w-full mt-8\" type=\"submit\"><span class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-h to-accent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-300\"></span><span class=\"relative\">Отправить заявку</span></button></form></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg-alt py-24 lg:py-32 relative bg-pattern\"><div class=\"w-full px-6 lg:px-12 xl:px-16\"><div class=\"relative inline-block\"><div class=\"absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 border-l-2 border-t-2 border-accent\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-3\"><div class=\"relative px-4 py-1.5 font-mono text-sm font-bold bg-accent/10 text-accent backdrop-blur-sm\" style=\"clip-path:polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%)\">02</div><div class=\"h-[2px] w-16 bg-accent/40\"></div></div><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight text-text\">Что мы можем</h2><div class=\"absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-6 h-6 border-r-2 border-b-2 border-accent/50\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mt-28\"><div class=\"reveal relative group\" style=\"transition-delay:0ms\"><div class=\"relative bg-white p-6 pt-32 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-4 left-4 w-8 h-8 border-l-2 border-b-2 border-accent/30 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><div class=\"inline-block bg-accent text-white font-mono 